articles.title: Former Miss America Runner-Up Shares Her Addiction Struggles - E! NEWS
articles.description: Cullen Johnson Hill, who was runner-up for Miss America 1995, shared an emotional video detailing her struggles with alcohol addiction and her 12-year sobriety journey.
articles.content:
